:v-model.description: The number of stars selected by default when the two-way binding is initialized
:v-model.description_zh: 双向绑定初始化时默认选中的星星数量

value.description: The number of stars is selected for two-way binding
value.description_zh: 双向绑定选择星星的数量

:count.description: The maximum number of stars that can be selected

readonly.description: Whether it is read-only or not

size.description: The size of the star, in rpx

inactiveColor.description: The color of the star is not selected

activeColor.description: The color of the selected star

minCount.description: The minimum number of stars selected

activeIcon.description: When selected, the icon name can only be the built-in icon of uView
activeIcon.description_zh: 选中时的图标名，只能为uView的内置图标

inactiveIcon.description: If the icon name is unchecked, it can only be the built-in icon of uView
inactiveIcon.description_zh: 未选中时的图标名，只能为uView的内置图标

touchable.description: Whether you can select a rating with a swipe gesture
touchable.description_zh: 是否可以通过滑动手势选择评分

events.name: change
events.description: Triggers when the selected star changes
events.description_zh: 选中的星星发生变化时触发
events.params: value：当前选中的星星的数量，如果使用v-model双向绑定方式，无需监听此事件
